data.description: GOLF COURSE VIEW AND OWN YOUR OWN LAND!  Welcome to 920 ORCHID ST in Orange Blossom Gardens. This lot is right on the golf course and gives you front row seating to all of the golf action while you relax on your screened in lanai enjoying the lush landscape of the backyard! The trees are maintained by The Villages - you just get to enjoy. This spacious 2B/2B home has a shingle roof, a workshop, ceiling fans and several sky lights to provide natural lighting, vaulted ceilings in the living room and master bedroom make it feel grand! The kitchen has updated appliances and tasteful counter tops making cooking in this kitchen a dream. The original carport was enclosed and added to the heated square footage making this unit one of the largest in the community! This well-maintained home has so much to offer. Optional memberships to the Orange Blossom Hills Golf and Country Club give you access to a shimmering blue pool, golf or tennis. Visit GolfTheVillages.com for more info. There is also a restaurant at the country club that is open to all residents regardless of membership.   You are a short golf cart ride away from Spanish Springs Square and not far from Lake Sumter Landing. Doctors, UF Hospital, shopping, golfing, pickleball courts, pools, recreation centers are all golf cart accessible.   Come see this home in person today!
